*xom-1.0-r4 (19 Nov 2007)

  19 Nov 2007; <alistair@gentoo.org> +xom-1.0-r4.ebuild:
  Revbump to fix usage of optional dependency.

  15 Nov 2007; Krzysiek Pawlik <nelchael@gentoo.org> xom-1.0-r3.ebuild:
  Stable on ppc, bug #142538.

  14 Nov 2007; Christian Faulhammer <opfer@gentoo.org> xom-1.0-r3.ebuild:
  stable x86, bug 142538

  13 Nov 2007; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org> metadata.xml,
  xom-1.0-r2.ebuild, xom-1.0-r3.ebuild:
  Shorten the DESCRIPTION by moving it to metadata.xml.

*xom-1.0-r3 (13 Nov 2007)

  13 Nov 2007; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org> +xom-1.0-r3.ebuild:
  dev-java/servletapi is only needed to build the examples to add examples use
  flag. Also now it does not get picked automatically from ant classpath.
  Reported in bug #142538.

  09 May 2007; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org> xom-1.0-r2.ebuild:
  Add ~ia64 wrt #160813

  08 Apr 2007; Markus Rothe <corsair@gentoo.org> xom-1.0-r2.ebuild:
  Stable on ppc64; bug #173207

  14 Feb 2007; Markus Rothe <corsair@gentoo.org> xom-1.0-r2.ebuild:
  Added ~ppc64

  13 Feb 2007; Vlastimil Babka <caster@gentoo.org> xom-1.0-r2.ebuild:
  Restrict icu4j dep to the right slot.

  09 Jan 2007; Vlastimil Babka <caster@gentoo.org> -xom-1.0-r1.ebuild:
  Gen-1 punt.

  09 Jan 2007; Steve Dibb <beandog@gentoo.org> xom-1.0-r2.ebuild:
  amd64 stable, bug 158047

  17 Dec 2006; Tobias Scherbaum <dertobi123@gentoo.org> xom-1.0-r2.ebuild:
  Stable on ppc wrt bug #158047.

  14 Dec 2006; Christian Faulhammer <opfer@gentoo.org> xom-1.0-r2.ebuild:
  stable x86, bug #158047

  09 Dec 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> xom-1.0-r2.ebuild:
  Add ~x86-fbsd keyword.

  30 Nov 2006; Vlastimil Babka <caster@gentoo.org> xom-1.0-r1.ebuild,
  xom-1.0-r2.ebuild:
  Update xerces dep for upcoming 2.6 slotmove.

  05 Oct 2006; Gustavo Zacarias <gustavoz@gentoo.org> xom-1.0-r1.ebuild,
  xom-1.0-r2.ebuild:
  Dropping sparc keywords, see #96229

*xom-1.0-r2 (15 Aug 2006)

  15 Aug 2006; Krzysiek Pawlik <nelchael@gentoo.org> +xom-1.0-r2.ebuild:
  Migrated to new Java build system.

  09 Dec 2005; Joshua Nichols <nichoj@gentoo.org> xom-1.0-r1.ebuild:
  Fixed invalid atom.

  09 Dec 2005; Joshua Nichols <nichoj@gentoo.org> xom-1.0-r1.ebuild:
  Loosened xerces dependency, in preparation for a new xerces release.

  09 Jul 2005; Thomas Matthijs <axxo@gentoo.org> xom-1.0-r1.ebuild:
  fix deps, some cleanup

  12 Jun 2005; Jason Wever <weeve@gentoo.org> xom-1.0-r1.ebuild:
  Added ~sparc keyword wrt bug #95859.

*xom-1.0-r1 (04 Jun 2005)

  04 Jun 2005; Jan Brinkmann <luckyduck@gentoo.org> -xom-1.0.ebuild,
  +xom-1.0-r1.ebuild:
  Updated reference to servletapi-2.3, we dont install a versioned servletapi
  jar any longer.

  28 Apr 2005; Jan Brinkmann <luckyduck@gentoo.org> xom-1.0.ebuild,
  -xom-1.0_beta5.ebuild, -xom-1.0_beta6.ebuild:
  1.0 stable on amd64, ppc and x86. did some cleanup and introduced support for
  the source useflag

